    ✨ [User Authentication and Management Implementation]
    
    🔐 Implemented user authentication and management features.
       - 🗃️ Created the 'users' table in the database to store user information.
       - 🌐 Implemented user registration, login, and password reset functionality.
       - 📝 Added user profile management features, allowing users to update their information.
       - 🔒 Set up user role management for admin and regular users.
    
    👥 Enabled Team management (optional) and configured related database tables.
       - 🏢 Created 'teams' and 'team_user' tables for team management.
       - 🚀 Implemented team creation, membership, and invitation features.
    
